            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "New determination of proton spectroscopic factors and",
                " reduced widths for be 8Be states in the 16.5-18.0 MeV",
                " excitation energy region via the study of the",
                " 7Li(3He,d)8Be transfer reaction at Elab = 20 MeV:",
                " implication for the 7Li(p,alpha)4He hydrogen",
                " burning reaction"
